<concept id="installation-installer-linux">
  <title>Choosing an Installer</title>
  <conbody>
    <p>You can install <ph keyref="product"/> on Linux using any of the following methods:</p>
    <ul>
      <li product="author developer editor svnClient">Install using the Linux installer.</li>
      <li product="author developer editor svnClient">Install using the Linux installer in
        unattended mode.</li>
      <li product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse">Install using the Update Site
        method.</li>
      <li product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse">Install using the Zip archive
        method.</li>
    </ul>
  </conbody>
